Package com.lutw.reports.dto

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    EntityDto
    Data transfer object for the report entity classes (components, beneficiaries lessons learned, media).
    FieldDto
    Data Transfer object for form fields populated from the database created from question and response objects
    FieldMapper
    Utility class that maps Report and Question domain objects into a Field data transfer object
    FormDto
    Data transfer object that holds a report and a list of fields
    FormMapper
    Utility class for mapping Form data transfer objects from Report domain objects
    QuestionDto
    Data transfer objects from Question domain objects.
    QuestionMapper
    QuestionMapper utility class for mapping Question objects to and from the respective QuestionDTO for use in the controller class or to be persisted
    QuestionSummary
    Data transfer object for the question summary objects
    SimpleSummary
    Data transfer object class for a simple value:description object
    TemplateDto
    Data transfer object that holds a list of questions for the form template editing page
